---
// Day Job — Overhaul (currently hidden in production but kept for parity).
---

<section id="aboutme" class="relative overflow-hidden" hidden>
  <div class="hero-glow opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 reveal flex-wrap">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500 tracking-wider uppercase">/ Day Job</span>
      <span
        class="font-mono text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 rounded uppercase tracking-wider"
        >NDA</span
      >
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-[10px] text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider"
      >
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        Shipping
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4 reveal">
      <a
        href="https://www.over-haul.com/resources?category_equal=%5B%22Blogs%22%5D#resource-block"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
        >Overhaul</a
      >
    </p>
    <h2
      class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight shimmer-text mb-4 reveal reveal-d1 max-w-3xl leading-[1.05]"
    >
      Real-time visibility. Secure by design.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-10 reveal reveal-d2">
      in-transit security · chain of custody · cargo that matters
    </p>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm reveal reveal-d3 max-w-md">
      Quiet build on secure, real-time supply-chain visibility — observability,
      chain-of-custody, and hardening for goods that can't afford to disappear.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
